
ID: 2
Title: Activating the ‘Send’ button with a click.

Priority:
High

Prerequisites:
N/A

Test type:
Positive (+)

Environment:
Windows 10, Chrome  80.0.3987.149

Description:
Test describes the results of an activating ‘Send’ button with a click.

Test scenario:
1.Open the chat.
2.In the messenger window enter:‘Hi Nicoletta. I need more info about our task. Could you give me more details?’
3.Click the ‘Send’ button.
4.Message has been sent.

The expected results:
1.Chat is opened.
2.In the messenger window is entered: ‘Hi Nicoletta. I need more info about our task. Could you give me more details?’
3.‘Send’ button is clicked.
4.Message has been sent.
